					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="600" height="405" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-143.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-143.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-143.png?resize=220%2C150&amp;ssl=1 220w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-143.png?resize=216%2C146&amp;ssl=1 216w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
