					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1626" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C488&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C975&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1300&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=230%2C146&amp;ssl=1 230w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 你有見過這麼會打球的貓咪嗎？一名女子在網路上分享自己父親與愛貓的神奇故事，日前 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/13/%e5%be%9e%e8%a8%8e%e5%8e%ad%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e5%88%b0%e6%84%9b%e4%b8%8a%ef%bc%9f%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e8%88%87%e8%80%81%e7%88%b6%e8%a6%aa%e7%ab%9f%e6%88%90%e4%ba%86%e5%85%b5%e4%b9%93%e7%90%83%e7%90%83/">從討厭貓咪到愛上？小貓與老父親竟成了兵乓球球友 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1626" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C488&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C975&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1300&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=230%2C146&amp;ssl=1 230w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/katja-anokhina-cGLfMt2T1BI-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>你有見過這麼會打球的貓咪嗎？一名女子在網路上分享自己父親與愛貓的神奇故事，日前她因工作關係將貓咪寄養在老家，原本擔心不喜愛貓咪的父親會因此感到排斥，卻沒想到意外見證了一場球友之間的特殊情誼，讓她感到十分震驚至今仍不敢置信。&nbsp;</p>



<p>據了解，這名女子飼養了一隻名字叫做「橘子」的小貓，她日前因工作關係只好暫時將愛貓寄養在老家，但她深知父親向來不喜歡貓咪，心中難免擔憂牠的適應情況，直到這天返家後卻發現父親對「橘子」的態度完全改觀，才揭開了這個隱藏的秘密。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="813" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/milada-vigerova-N8lcQwgx4so-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C813&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-240797" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/milada-vigerova-N8lcQwgx4so-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/milada-vigerova-N8lcQwgx4so-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/milada-vigerova-N8lcQwgx4so-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/milada-vigerova-N8lcQwgx4so-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/milada-vigerova-N8lcQwgx4so-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/milada-vigerova-N8lcQwgx4so-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">「橘子」憑著迅速反應和父親對打兵乓球，拉近了與長輩之間的距離<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>原來「橘子」天生就擁有神奇的隱藏技能，牠不僅能和父親有來有回地對打乒乓球，甚至還懂得如何殺球，靠著自身的反應時不時擊出高難度回擊，這項技能幫助牠迅速地拉近了與長輩的距離，還成功讓原本不喜歡寵物的爸爸成為牠的最佳球友。&nbsp;</p>



<p>女子將愛貓與父親的有趣互動分享至網路上，迅速引起網友們熱烈討論，不少人大讚「橘子」的運動天賦，也感嘆道「動物與人們之間的隔閡是能夠化解的」、「貓貓憑本事討人喜愛」、「有沒有可能橘子在故意放水」、「牠打的不是兵乓，打的是人情世故」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/13/%e5%be%9e%e8%a8%8e%e5%8e%ad%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e5%88%b0%e6%84%9b%e4%b8%8a%ef%bc%9f%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e8%88%87%e8%80%81%e7%88%b6%e8%a6%aa%e7%ab%9f%e6%88%90%e4%ba%86%e5%85%b5%e4%b9%93%e7%90%83%e7%90%83/">從討厭貓咪到愛上？小貓與老父親竟成了兵乓球球友 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
